","m":"along with Lakshmana"},{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"महादेववचः","m":"Lord MahaDeva's words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"listening"},{"d":"विमानशिखरस्थस्य","m":"seated on top of the aerial car"},{"d":"पितुः","m":"father"},{"d":"प्रणामम्","m":"salutations"},{"d":"चकार","m":"offered"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"दीप्यमानंस्वयालक्ष्मविरजोऽम्भरधारिणम् ।लक्ष्मणेनसहभ्रात्राददर्शपितरंप्रभुः","trans":"Raghava with his younger brother Lakshmana saw his father who was effulgent, blazing and adorned in white clothes.","words":[{"d":"प्रभुः","m":"Lord"},{"d":"भ्रात्रा","m":"brother"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणेन","m":"with Lakshmana"},{"d":"स्वया","m":"you"},{"d":"लक्ष्म","m":"effulgent"},{"d":"दीप्यमानम्","m":"blazing"},{"d":"विरजोऽम्बरधारिणम्","m":"adorned in white clothes"},{"d":"पितरम्","m":"father"},{"d":"ददर्श","m":"saw"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"हर्षेणमहताविष्टोविमनस्थोमहीपतिः ।प्राणैःप्रियतरंदृष्टवापुत्रंदशरथस्तदा आरोप्याङ्केमहबाहुर्वरासनगतःप्रभुः ।बाहुभ्यांसम्परिष्वज्यततोवाक्यंसमाददे","trans":"Then Dasaratha, the ruler of the world, seated in an elevated seat in the aerial car, seeing his son who was dearer than life to him, extremely rejoiced and made Raghava sit on his lap, embraced him, and started speaking as follows.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"विमानस्थः","m":"aerial car's"},{"d":"महीपतिः","m":"ruler of the world"},{"d":"प्रभुः","m":"Lord"},{"d":"वरासनगतः","m":"elevated seat"},{"d":"दशरथः","m":"Dasharatha"},{"d":"प्राणैः","m":"life"},{"d":"प्रियतरम्","m":"dearer"},{"d":"पुत्रम्","m":"son"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"महता","m":"extremely"},{"d":"हर्षेण","m":"rejoiced"},{"d":"आविष्टः","m":"making him sit"},{"d":"अङ्के","m":"on his lap"},{"d":"आरोप्य","m":"seated"},{"d":"बाहुभ्याम्","m":"many"},{"d":"सम्परिष्वज्य","m":"embracing"},{"d":"ततः","m":"these"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"समाददे","m":"started"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"हर्षेणमहताविष्टोविमनस्थोमहीपतिः ।प्राणैःप्रियतरंदृष्टवापुत्रंदशरथस्तदा आरोप्याङ्केमहबाहुर्वरासनगतःप्रभुः ।बाहुभ्यांसम्परिष्वज्यततोवाक्यंसमाददे","trans":"Then Dasaratha, the ruler of the world, seated in an elevated seat in the aerial car, seeing his son who was dearer than life to him, extremely rejoiced and made Raghava sit on his lap, embraced him, and started speaking as follows.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"विमानस्थः","m":"aerial car's"},{"d":"महीपतिः","m":"ruler of the world"},{"d":"प्रभुः","m":"Lord"},{"d":"वरासनगतः","m":"elevated seat"},{"d":"दशरथः","m":"Dasharatha"},{"d":"प्राणैः","m":"life"},{"d":"प्रियतरम्","m":"dearer"},{"d":"पुत्रम्","m":"son"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"महता","m":"extremely"},{"d":"हर्षेण","m":"rejoiced"},{"d":"आविष्टः","m":"making him sit"},{"d":"अङ्के","m":"on his lap"},{"d":"आरोप्य","m":"seated"},{"d":"बाहुभ्याम्","m":"many"},{"d":"सम्परिष्वज्य","m":"embracing"},{"d":"ततः","m":"these"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"समाददे","m":"started"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"न मेस्वर्गोबहुमतस्सम्मानश्चसुरर्षभैः ।त्वयारामविहीनस्यसत्यंप्रतिशृणोमिते","trans":"\"Rama separated from you, even the suras and sages honouring me in heaven does not give me happiness. It is true and I promise.\"","words":[{"d":"राम","m":"Rama"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"विहीनस्य","m":"having got separated"},{"d":"मे","m":"me"},{"d":"स्वर्गः","m":"heaven"},{"d":"न बहुमतः","m":"by several"},{"d":"सुरर्षभैः","m":"suras"},{"d":"सम्मानश्च","m":"honouring"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"सत्यम्","m":"true"},{"d":"प्रतिशृणोमि","m":"promise"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"अद्यत्वांनिहतामित्रंदृष्टवासम्पूर्णमानसम् ।निस्तीर्णवनवासं च प्रीतिरासीत्परामम","trans":"\"Today the enemies are killed, and you have completed the exile. I am fully satisfied and experiencing joyfulness on seeing you.\"","words":[{"d":"अद्य","m":"today"},{"d":"निहतामित्रम्","m":"enemies killed"},{"d":"सम्पूर्णमानसम्","m":"fully satisfied in mind"},{"d":"निस्तीर्णवनवासंच","m":"completed the exile"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"on seeing"},{"d":"मम","m":"to me"},{"d":"परा","m":"very"},{"d":"प्रीतिः","m":"joyful"},{"d":"आसीत्","m":"experiencing